name: DendroRithms
description: **DendroRithms is a decentralised art installation inspired by tree growth rings.** Every Dendro is uniquely generated from user input using an interactive minting process. Buyers collectively decide the rarity and evolution of the artwork.

name: unsigned_algorithms
description: The first algorithmically generated art living on Cardano. Mathematically derived and designed, generated using computers and advanced algorithms.

name: Rorschach Algorithm Beasts
description: A collection of 999 hand-selected procedurally generated creatures. Creepy or cute, a frog, a bee or Cthulhu, Rorschach Algorithm Beasts come in various unique shapes. Infinity-evolution: Your NFT evolves continuously a little bit every day - forever!

name: Butterfly Effect
description: Animated crypto-butterflies based on real mathematical equations used in chaos theory.

name: Implicit Squiggles
description: Abstract faces rendered with differential equations using the pareidolia effect.

name: AI on-chain
description: First fully on-chain generative AI NFT, containing the neural network evaluation code and all weights and biases in the NFT on-chain. Weights were trained with a different set of input images for each NFT.
